End-to-end testing mainly covers serious issues and core data links, which is helpful in two ways:
1. Automate regression testing before release, so that serious issues can be discovered in advance;
2. Perform regular inspections online as an aid to online monitoring.

It mainly includes the following points:
1. Improve the readability of alarm cards so that the problem cause can be quickly identified from the alarm message;
2. Have automatic response capability, when a problem occurs, automatically pull in groups or individuals based on problem classification, and accelerate problem handling;
3. Have certain automatic positioning capability, and perform related queries based on problem characteristics to help locate recent releases.
